item.description:
Today's Workout: 3 sets 345x5 squat, 5 sets 205x5 bench, 5 sets 185x5 barbell rows. #StrongLifts5x5

Only 3 squat sets today because I'm lifting again tomorrow.

Missed Tues lift due to Neo community call. Missed Wed lift because (checks notes) I overslept. Missing Sat lift for Labor day weekend plans. So back to back Thurs and Fri only way to get in multiple lifts this week.
